{
  "texts": [
    "The orange colours represent negative coefficients, while the green ones represent positive coefficients.",
    "The more extreme the value, the more saturated the colour.",
    "A linear progression was not always followed by the variables that were examined in this study.",
    "For instance, \"reconstruction country\" cannot be numerically compared with \"game engine.\"",
    "Whenever possible, the data were coded from lower to higher, assigning lower values to variables with lower technological complexity."
  ]
}